// launch.json - Configures debugging setup for the TMS570 LaunchPad
// Defines how VS Code connects to the hardware for debugging
// Uses TI's ARM GDB for debugging the target
// Creator: Max Kulick

{
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "configurations": [
        {
            "name": "TMS570 Debug",
            "type": "cppdbg",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "${workspaceRoot}/build/TMS570_FREERTOS.out",
            "args": [],
            "stopAtEntry": true,
            "cwd": "${workspaceRoot}",
            "environment": [],
            "externalConsole": false,
            "MIMode": "gdb",
            "miDebuggerPath": "C:/ti/ccs2010/ccs/tools/compiler/ti-cgt-armllvm_4.0.2.LTS/bin/tiarmgdb",
            "setupCommands": [
                {
                    "description": "Enable pretty-printing for gdb",
                    "text": "-enable-pretty-printing",
                    "ignoreFailures": true
                }
            ],
            "preLaunchTask": "Build"
        }
    ]
}